lead_paragraph: Jabari Blash hit two of San Diego's six homers, and the Padres beat Triple-A El Paso 13-9 in an exhibition on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Padres Hit 6 Homers in Exhibition Win Over Triple-A El Paso
